&lt;p style=&quot;color:  (33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: bolder;&quot;&gt;Given word :&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;FOREFOOT&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;color:  (33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: bolder;&quot;&gt;According to the question :&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;color:  (33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;1) Each vowel&amp;nbsp;is changed to the following letter in the English alphabetical series&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;color:  (33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;&amp;rArr; Vowels is the word &amp;#39;&lt;span style=&quot;color:  (33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;FOREFOOT&lt;/span&gt;&amp;#39; :-&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;

