		&lt;/tr&gt;
	&lt;/tbody&gt;
&lt;/table&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;color:  (33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;Here, the transformation will be &amp;quot;FPRFFPPT&amp;quot;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;color:  (33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;2) Each consonant is changed to the previous letter in the English alphabetical series&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;color:  (33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;&amp;rArr; Consonants is the word &amp;#39;&lt;span style=&quot;color:  (33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;FOREFOOT&lt;/span&gt;&amp;#39; :-&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;table border=&quot;1&quot; cellpadding=&quot;1&quot; cellspacing=&quot;1&quot; style=&quot;color:  (33, 37, 41); width: 350px;&quot;&gt;
	&lt;tbody&gt;
		&lt;tr&gt;
			&lt;td style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: bolder;&quot;&gt;Consonants&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
